 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p3041ds.dts  | 30 ++++++++++++++++++------------
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p4080ds.dts  | 30 ++++++++++++++++++------------
 3 files changed, 54 insertions(+), 36 deletions(-)

